data.description: Imagine if you will, the most happy and enchanting Cul-De-Sac to live in was YOURS!! 4 Bedrooms, 2 &1/2 Bathrooms. Electric FPLC, Fenced in private yard, with Jungle Gym, and shed. Vaulted ceilings, skylights in living room. 2nd Kitchen in lower level! 1st floor laundry. Many updates too many to mention, include: All newer Windows , Garbage disposal, stove, hot water heater, A/C, water softener, water hose spicket, dishwasher, garage door, all 2022 and roof repairs, 2021. (many more not mentioned in Documents).
